paragraphs.title: Getting the feedback documents for topics
paragraphs.text:
import scala.io.Source
import scala.util.parsing.json._

val project = "6_topics_nd_1"

val topics = Array("BKRT", "CHAIR1", "MEET1", "CFO1", "CEO1", "DDEAL")


def getTopicData(project: String, topic: String): String = {
    
    val html = Source.fromURL("http://whyaron:9000/api/searchQuestionableDocs/fnr/"+project+"?filter=label:"+topic+"&fromIndex=0&pageSize=50&sortField=uncertaintyScore&sortOrder=desc")
    val s = html.mkString
    
    val json = JSON.parseFull(s)
    
    val map: Map[String,Any] = json.get.asInstanceOf[Map[String, Any]]
    
    val docs: List[Any] = map.get("docs").get.asInstanceOf[List[Any]]
    
    val docsMap = docs.map( docMap => {
        val doc: Map[String,Any] = docMap.asInstanceOf[Map[String,Any]]
        val id: String = doc.get("id").get.asInstanceOf[String]
        val label: String = doc.get("label").get.asInstanceOf[String]
        val source: String = doc.get("source").get.asInstanceOf[String].replaceAll(",", ".")
        val score: Double = doc.get("score").get.asInstanceOf[Double]
        (id, label, source, score)
    })
    
    var csvString: String = ""
    
    
    docsMap.foreach(doc => {
        val row = doc._1 + "," + doc._2 + ",," + doc._3 + ",true," + doc._4 + "\n"
        csvString = csvString + row
    })
    
    csvString
}

var csvString: String = ""

topics.foreach(topic => {
    csvString = csvString + getTopicData(project, topic)
})

println(csvString)
